title: Sector Shift Continues Out Of Healthcare Stocks
text: October 23, 2015 at 00:28 AM EDT Sector Shift Continues Out Of Healthcare Stocks The Dow Jones soared 1.87% today and other key indices followed up 1.6% in an impressive rally that accelerated after hours with earnings from Amazon, Alphabet Cl A, Facebook and Microsoft that carried these names another 7-10% after hours.
